## 🛣️ Suggested Build Order (Roadmap)

### Phase 1 — Core UX Fixes (Do First)
1. ✅ Message date separators
2. ✅ Unread message badges
3. ✅ Multi-line textarea input
4. ✅ Color gradient avatars (replace letter-only)
5. ✅ Consecutive message grouping (no repeat avatar)

### Phase 2 — Social Features
6. Message reactions (emoji reactions)
7. Message reply / quote
8. Last seen status
9. User profile & avatar upload

### Phase 3 — Power Features
10. Message search
11. Notification bell + in-app toasts
12. Voice messages
13. Room management (rename, leave, persist)

### Phase 4 — Wow Features
14. Themes / dark-light mode toggle
15. Link previews
16. File/media gallery
17. AI `@nexus` bot
18. Pinned messages

---

## 🔧 Technical Debt to Fix

| Issue | Fix |
|---|---|
| Messages limited to 200 per room | Add pagination / infinite scroll |
| No JWT verification on socket connections | Verify token on `connection` event |
| `window.confirm()` for delete | Replace with a custom animated modal |
| No input validation on frontend | Add Zod or Yup schema validation |
| No error boundaries | Wrap components in React `ErrorBoundary` |
| Rooms not persisted (lost on refresh) | Save joined rooms in localStorage or DB |
| No `rooms` table in DB | Create rooms table for metadata |
| Rate limiting only on auth | Add rate limiting on file upload too |
| File size limit not enforced | Add `limits: { fileSize: 10 * 1024 * 1024 }` to multer |

